id: pm-4dtf
title: Add integration test for schema add-type / remove-type round-trip with governance.workflow_enforcement
description: "Schema customization (pm schema add-type, remove-type, add-status, remove-status) was shipped in PR #106 (2026-06-03). Unit tests cover settings-validator, item-type-definition, and schema-command. There is a governance-presets.integration.spec.ts for preset workflows but no integration test for the full schema customization round-trip: add custom type, create item of that type, enforce workflow transitions, remove type with items warning, then verify it is gone."
