resolution: "Integration test drives pm schema add-type Spike -> pm create Spike -> set governance-workflow-enforcement strict + per-type workflows (schema/workflows.json) -> rejected disallowed transition (open->done) -> allowed transition (open->in_progress) -> pm schema remove-type (warns items_using_type:2) -> verify type gone (schema show unknown_item_type, create rejected) -> orphaned items no longer resolvable."
expected_result: End-to-end schema-customization round-trip with workflow enforcement is covered by an integration test using sandboxed PM_PATH.
actual_result: "1 integration test, 6 lifecycle phases asserted; passes against dist CLI."
